{"operation":"llm.complete_task_with_tools","payload":{"agentId":"6961092d-82fa-4591-bd84-98a2cebb163a","agentName":"Scout","baseUrl":"https://api.deepseek.com","choice":"[{\"text\":\"**Research Summary: Product Planning Best Practices & Industry Cases**\\n\\nCompleted comprehensive research on product planning methodologies. Key findings include:\\n\\n**Core Best Practices:**\\n1. **Strategic Alignment** - Link product plans to business objectives and market opportunities\\n2. **Customer-Centricity** - Base decisions on user research and continuous feedback\\n3. **Agile Methodologies** - Implement Scrum, Kanban, or hybrid approaches for flexibility\\n4. **Data-Driven Prioritization** - Use frameworks like RICE, MoSCoW, Kano model\\n5. **Cross-functional Collaboration** - Engage engineering, design, marketing, sales teams\\n\\n**Industry Frameworks Identified:**\\n- ProductPlan's 6-step process (Discover → Deploy)\\n- Agile product planning with backlog management\\n- OKR-based strategic alignment\\n- Lean Startup build-measure-learn cycles\\n- SAFe for enterprise scaling\\n- Design thinking principles\\n\\n**Success Factors:**\\n- Clear product vision and strategy\\n- MVP-focused development\\n- Continuous market validation\\n- Balanced short/long-term planning\\n- Integrated quality assurance\\n\\n**Common Pitfalls to Avoid:**\\n- Feature creep without prioritization\\n- Technical debt accumulation\\n- Poor stakeholder communication\\n- Rigid planning without adaptability\\n\\n**Tools & Templates Recommended:**\\n- Product roadmaps\\n- User story mapping\\n- Feature prioritization matrices\\n- Release planning calendars\\n- Stakeholder communication plans\\n\\n**Recommendation:** Adopt a hybrid approach combining agile execution with strategic planning, using data-driven prioritization and continuous stakeholder alignment.\\n\\nDelegate @Builder: Develop product planning templates and roadmap structures based on research findings.\"}]","maxTokens":2000,"maxTurns":540,"messageId":null,"model":"deepseek-chat","providerId":"deepseek","providerType":"DeepSeek","sessionId":"6f907aca-3299-45a7-a38c-c238a691a534","taskCardId":"ca94b74c-49a6-41f5-a53b-4c795d7b6290","temperature":0.8,"usage":{"cached_input_tokens":33536,"input_tokens":33805,"output_tokens":329,"total_tokens":34134},"workGroupId":"32c79005-71dc-4969-8aaa-9f59d7511499"},"phase":"completion_response","timestamp":"2026-03-10T01:43:49.077839+00:00"}
{"operation":"llm.complete_task_with_tools","payload":{"model":"deepseek-chat","providerId":"deepseek","providerType":"DeepSeek","sessionId":"6f907aca-3299-45a7-a38c-c238a691a534","summary":"**Research Summary: Product Planning Best Practices & Industry Cases**\n\nCompleted comprehensive research on product planning methodologies. Key findings include:\n\n**Core Best Practices:**\n1. **Strategic Alignment** - Link product plans to business objectives and market opportunities\n2. **Customer-Centricity** - Base decisions on user research and continuous feedback\n3. **Agile Methodologies** - Implement Scrum, Kanban, or hybrid approaches for flexibility\n4. **Data-Driven Prioritization** - Use frameworks like RICE, MoSCoW, Kano model\n5. **Cross-functional Collaboration** - Engage engineering, design, marketing, sales teams\n\n**Industry Frameworks Identified:**\n- ProductPlan's 6-step process (Discover → Deploy)\n- Agile product planning with backlog management\n- OKR-based strategic alignment\n- Lean Startup build-measure-learn cycles\n- SAFe for enterprise scaling\n- Design thinking principles\n\n**Success Factors:**\n- Clear product vision and strategy\n- MVP-focused development\n- Continuous market validation\n- Balanced short/long-term planning\n- Integrated quality assurance\n\n**Common Pitfalls to Avoid:**\n- Feature creep without prioritization\n- Technical debt accumulation\n- Poor stakeholder communication\n- Rigid planning without adaptability\n\n**Tools & Templates Recommended:**\n- Product roadmaps\n- User story mapping\n- Feature prioritization matrices\n- Release planning calendars\n- Stakeholder communication plans\n\n**Recommendation:** Adopt a hybrid approach combining agile execution with strategic planning, using data-driven prioritization and continuous stakeholder alignment.\n\nDelegate @Builder: Develop product planning templates and roadmap structures based on research findings.","taskCardId":"ca94b74c-49a6-41f5-a53b-4c795d7b6290","toolEventCoun